{"tid":1627634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"預留11月24號 做孝子!!!","createTime":"2019-10-05T16:53:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:09:36.000Z","uid":53352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"870427191beb6edcd96460163df9e368f96438e7","tid":1627634,"uid":53352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:53:10.000Z","msg":"而家諗遠少少先<br />\n當11月24可以選區議會<br />\n你知唔知個日最重要做咩丫?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期日當然係做孝子送禮物俾父母啦"},{"pid":"75cfed5712f8434e29c99d8415bc53f93758f24e","tid":1627634,"uid":53352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:54:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"40b7b05b5faf9964c669fd52bf4bd2240744e34b","tid":1627634,"uid":53352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:54:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9901eaa98bd04fe2f64209ab3b80b92ba75759f1","tid":1627634,"uid":53352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:55:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d7fe3559bbb574dce76a1285a1270759a334c8d4","tid":1627634,"uid":53352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:55:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8969b9d70cca6cc75698f7a06ed0c66d04515edd","tid":1627634,"uid":53352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:55:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4431775e3f8c386c31ad96d3b333e307d45cc4d1","tid":1627634,"uid":53352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:55:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cb12d0b1b8fee1bc9ac2db40a0d95996a06fdbf4","tid":1627634,"uid":319687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:30:31.000Z","msg":"<strong>對方使用緊急法去立曚面法</strong><br />\n<strong><ins>目的:</ins></strong><br />\n引發更多怒氣, 更多人出街<br />\n1, 使政府立緊急法合理化<br />\n2, 繞過正常程序, 為日後透過緊急法立其它法鋪路 (如凍結資產, 限制通訊, 限制外匯)<br />\n3, 以此為藉口, 推遲或取消區議會, 使原本100%己敗的選舉重新定位<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>解決方案:</ins></strong><br />\n<strong>1, 拉一派, 打一派, </strong>儘量透過這次立緊急法同曚面法帶來的影響争取更多團體的支持, 例如受影響的商家, 目標對準林鄭班子<br />\n<strong>2, 敵進我退</strong>, 當我們知道對家的棋路之後, 就要往<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">相反</span></strong>的方向做, 對家期望會更亂, 我地就要更有秩序, 對家想跟我們決一死戰, 我們就要休息<br />\n<strong>3, 虛實並用</strong>, 不戰而屈人之兵, 若一個吹得起既風而鈎到過百隻狗, 最後班狗無功而回, 不費一兵一卒, 一蚊都唔使比。同樣係政治, 經濟, 媒體, 文宣勇武, 和理非各項必須虛實並用, 目標係不戰而屈人之兵, 以小本勝大本, 令對方管治成本大福上升, 以消耗他們龐大的資源<br />\n<strong>4, 令對方各員產生恐懼</strong>, 不論任何方法, 讓敵方望而遠之, 要他們確切知道幫港共政權做事是有很重的代價"},{"pid":"3d70d044c2a8f606d1d2516e7cb5ed304d424f59","tid":1627634,"uid":53352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:05:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1157869a031ccb623ba0af7131ff3a7773dd4683","tid":1627634,"uid":53352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:05:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2d21aa54ee024bb2071ffaf0830a902ef1bde3c9","tid":1627634,"uid":53352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:09:36.000Z","msg":"push"}]}